OL,3,CAntarctica: Following Shackleton's
OL,4,CEndurance mission 100 years on
OL,6,FScientists are collecting data from a
OL,7,Fnearby glacier, but there's also an
OL,8,Femotional connection.
OL,10,FIt was on Elephant Island that
OL,11,FShackleton's men made their base after
OL,12,Fbeing stranded when the Endurance was
OL,13,Fcrushed by ice and sank in 1915.
OL,15,FIn total, they survived nearly two
OL,16,Fyears on the ice before being rescued
OL,17,F- in one of the most daring missions
OL,18,Fin polar history.
