OL,3,CAntarctica: Following Shackleton's
OL,4,CEndurance mission 100 years on
OL,6,FNo British research ship has been this
OL,7,Ffar south at this time of year since
OL,8,Fthen. Now, it's up to Captain Will
OL,9,FWhatley to get us there - to mark the
OL,10,Fsouthern winter solstice, or
OL,11,Fmidwinter, and make a new chapter in
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,F"I love reading polar history while in
OL,15,Fthe Polar Region," Captain Will tells
OL,16,Fme. He first became interested in
OL,17,FShackleton's adventures as a 19-year-
OL,18,Fold, joining the British Antarctic
OL,19,FSurvey. Now, just turned 36, he's the
OL,20,Fman in charge.
