OL,3,CAntarctica: Following Shackleton's
OL,4,CEndurance mission 100 years on
OL,6,FA lot has changed since the Endurance.
OL,7,FThe hull of the RRS Sir David
OL,8,FAttenborough is made of inch-thick
OL,9,Fsteel, not wood, for starters. Even
OL,10,Fso, they have to plan for the worst.
OL,12,FThe ship has several lifeboats. The
OL,13,Ftwo largest can each hold all 90
OL,14,Fpassengers in a squeeze ` and it would
OL,15,Fcertainly be that tight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
