OL,3,CAntarctica: Following Shackleton's
OL,4,CEndurance mission 100 years on
OL,6,FThere are two chemical mini toilets,
OL,7,Frations that look like firelights, and
OL,8,Fsea-sickness tablets, which are
OL,9,Fmandatory on the bobbing boat. It's
OL,10,Ffair to say survival takes priority
OL,11,Fover comfort.
OL,13,FIf the sea is frozen over, the ship is
OL,14,Falso equipped with enough camping gear
OL,15,Fto sleep and survive in the ice for 20
OL,16,Fdays. Hundreds of thousands of pounds'
OL,17,Fworth of super-warm clothing for 100
OL,18,Fpeople is stored onboard - hopefully
OL,19,Fnever to be used.
