OL,3,CAntarctica: Following Shackleton's
OL,4,CEndurance mission 100 years on
OL,6,FCadets showed me the meticulously
OL,7,Fmaintained safety equipment: bags
OL,8,Ffilled with dried food, water
OL,9,Fpurification tablets, shovels, and
OL,10,Feven giant, vicious-looking saws.
OL,12,FThe gruesome end of Arctic explorers
OL,13,Faboard Erebus and Terror springs to
OL,14,Fmind, but I'm assured these tools are
OL,15,Ffor cutting ice blocks, not human
OL,16,Fflesh!
OL,18,FWe laugh about the grim prospects of
OL,19,Fanything going wrong, but it's
OL,20,Freassuring to know safety is taken
OL,21,Fextremely seriously.
